data.description: Welcome to the Northside... Looking for an amazing home with GREAT Airbnb potential? Or a beautiful Waterfront Home overlooking deep water to fish, kayak, jet-ski, boating on the river, or just a relaxing sunset outing? This exquisite secluded deep waterfront beauty with electric Boat Lift, Dock, Work-Shed and custom back deck, is a must see. With a possible 4th Bedroom/now Formal Lvg Rm, an Open Floor Plan and Granite Countertops with Stainless-Steel Appliances in the kitchen with high ceilings, this gem won't last long. Washer/Dryer does not convey with the sale of the Property. Not many deep water sites left in this area. CRAB & SHRIMP GALORE! DONT WAIT & MISS OUT!
